text: Now, did you enjoy that session? Or did you enjoy that session, sweetie?
Good. I'm so glad. Let me get you out now. You've been tied up for a while now, huh?
Oh, just normally I don't do the knot in the rope like this.
I might have been a bit preoccupied with you, huh?
That's not like me to make such a mistake.
My nails are making this harder than usual. I knew I shouldn't have gotten them this long.
Do you want now? Oh, no. I just can't cut the rope. That's not the right thing to do, silly.
These ropes are invaluable to me. If I went cutting through all my equipment, I'd have none left now.
Would I? Your skin isn't too marked at all, either.
I made sure not to make them too tight, at least.
So, just give me a few moments while I wrestle away with this.
I'll have you out in no time. I promise.
I've had some sessions run over 12 hours, so it's not like your limbs are gonna fall off or anything.
My goodness. Did it really make such a big mistake?
I wonder when I did it. Was it when you started doing that thing I like?
Normally I'm so focused, so I guess this situation is a compliment to you, after all.
Wait, no, I didn't get it.
Oh, no. That's not it, either.
Give me a good little nod.
Ugh, I didn't do anything, either.
I need to get my nails shorter next time.
I have to be somewhere, so...
